1
00:00:50,049 --> 00:00:52,469
DRAMA INI HANYA REKAAN

2
00:00:52,552 --> 00:00:54,971
RAKAMAN MEMATUHI GARIS PANDUAN

3
00:01:18,787 --> 00:01:19,954
Na-hyun.

4
00:01:22,373 --> 00:01:23,374
Han Na-hyun!

5
00:01:25,043 --> 00:01:26,711
Apa lagi?

6
00:01:26,795 --> 00:01:27,879
Mak!

7
00:01:28,421 --> 00:01:30,256
Bukankah kamu kata ada kerja sekolah?

8
00:01:30,882 --> 00:01:33,635
Mana Na-hyun yang sibuk belajar
sampai tak boleh tolong mak?

9
00:01:33,718 --> 00:01:35,595
Bukanlah, mak.

10
00:01:37,514 --> 00:01:39,140
Tadi saya dah buat kerja sekolah.

11
00:01:39,682 --> 00:01:41,768
Betul. Tak tipu.

12
00:01:41,851 --> 00:01:43,353
Sudahlah, mak dah tahu.

13
00:01:44,062 --> 00:01:46,481
Cakaplah kalau mak datang!

14
00:01:46,564 --> 00:01:48,983
Kenapa salahkan kakak pula?

15
00:01:49,067 --> 00:01:51,027
Sudah, kamu berdua.

16
00:01:51,111 --> 00:01:52,695
- Dia mula dulu.
- Dia mula dulu.

17
00:01:52,779 --> 00:01:54,656
Sampai bila kamu nak bergaduh begini?

18
00:01:54,739 --> 00:01:56,074
Sampai tua dan beruban nanti?

19
00:02:05,875 --> 00:02:09,379
{\an8}HAN NA-HYUN, HAN SO-HYUN

20
00:02:17,220 --> 00:02:18,972
20 OGOS 1997
PAKAI BAJU HUJAN…

21
00:02:26,521 --> 00:02:27,522
12 OGOS 2008

22
00:02:31,985 --> 00:02:33,278
So-hyun.

23
00:02:34,404 --> 00:02:35,947
Kamu masih kecil.

24
00:02:37,157 --> 00:02:39,868
PELAJAR SEKOLAH MELURU KE JALAN

25
00:02:53,423 --> 00:02:54,257
{\an8}Wah.

26
00:02:55,258 --> 00:02:56,759
{\an8}Cantiknya bintang.

27
00:03:04,058 --> 00:03:05,268
Betul-betul datang.

28
00:03:19,240 --> 00:03:21,784
Maaf. Awak…

29
00:03:29,584 --> 00:03:31,085
HAN SO-HYUN 19 TAHUN
7 JULAI 2012

30
00:03:44,849 --> 00:03:45,725
Apa itu?

31
00:03:49,187 --> 00:03:50,730
Budak-budak jahat.

32
00:03:56,027 --> 00:03:57,070
Alamak.

33
00:03:58,112 --> 00:04:00,073
Dia baru saja sampai.

34
00:04:04,327 --> 00:04:05,870
Mati sajalah.

35
00:04:06,371 --> 00:04:09,707
Kau memang suka dibelasah, ya?

36
00:04:10,541 --> 00:04:11,709
Hoi, sudah!

37
00:04:15,880 --> 00:04:16,965
Dia nak apa?

38
00:04:17,548 --> 00:04:21,594
Tiga lawan satu? Mana adil.

39
00:04:22,595 --> 00:04:24,222
Kalau dah mabuk, jangan sibuk.

40
00:04:25,265 --> 00:04:27,809
Berjalan pun tak betul,
ada hati nak betulkan orang,

41
00:04:27,892 --> 00:04:28,726
pak cik.

42
00:04:29,644 --> 00:04:31,145
Pak cik?

43
00:04:31,813 --> 00:04:33,731
Apa kau cakap?

44
00:04:33,815 --> 00:04:35,525
Pak cik ini dah mabuk teruk.

45
00:04:36,234 --> 00:04:37,443
Kena ajar sikit.

46
00:04:59,048 --> 00:05:02,302
TAEKWONDO HORANG
SIJIL KEPUJIAN

47
00:05:05,722 --> 00:05:08,057
Encik tak boleh buat begini.

48
00:05:08,141 --> 00:05:10,018
Atau sebab saya muda?

49
00:05:11,894 --> 00:05:13,146
Muka saja muda.

50
00:05:15,356 --> 00:05:17,650
Mereka pukul budak itu beramai-ramai!

51
00:05:17,734 --> 00:05:19,736
Senyap. Ini balai polis.

52
00:05:19,819 --> 00:05:20,987
- Pergi dulu.
- Okey.

53
00:05:21,612 --> 00:05:24,198
Encik! Tunggu!

54
00:05:24,282 --> 00:05:25,283
Diamlah!

55
00:05:28,911 --> 00:05:30,663
Memekak saja!

56
00:05:31,289 --> 00:05:34,334
Aku nak tidur pun susah.

57
00:05:36,169 --> 00:05:37,462
Jadi lagi.

58
00:05:37,545 --> 00:05:39,881
Aduh, sakitnya hati!

59
00:05:41,507 --> 00:05:42,508
Pak cik pun di sini.

60
00:05:43,217 --> 00:05:44,510
Baguslah.

61
00:05:44,594 --> 00:05:47,180
Pak cik nampak mereka pukul
seorang budak, bukan?

62
00:05:47,764 --> 00:05:48,765
Nampak.

63
00:05:49,557 --> 00:05:53,978
Betulkah awak lawan
tiga budak itu seorang diri?

64
00:05:57,815 --> 00:06:01,527
Mestilah, saya belajar taekwondo
sejak kecil lagi.

65
00:06:03,029 --> 00:06:06,240
Mereka pun ada di sini?

66
00:06:06,324 --> 00:06:08,326
Gilakah? Cakap seorang diri.

67
00:06:09,160 --> 00:06:12,789
Ada, saya minta polis tangkap
sebab mereka langgar undang-undang.

68
00:06:13,331 --> 00:06:14,791
Penjenayah kena dihukum.

69
00:06:16,459 --> 00:06:19,003
Awak lurus sangat.

70
00:06:20,088 --> 00:06:22,090
Bukan masalah lurus!

71
00:06:22,173 --> 00:06:24,300
Kalau tak tegas dengan jenayah,

72
00:06:24,383 --> 00:06:27,720
dunia boleh huru-hara
sekelip mata, pak cik.

73
00:06:28,346 --> 00:06:31,933
Matlamat saya nak jadikan
dunia ini adil dan indah,

74
00:06:32,016 --> 00:06:34,894
hidup tenteram mengikut undang-undang

75
00:06:35,520 --> 00:06:39,148
dan orang saling menghormati.

76
00:06:40,441 --> 00:06:43,069
Sebab itu awak nak jadi peguam.

77
00:06:43,152 --> 00:06:47,031
Sebab itulah, saya tak boleh berlembut
walaupun kesalahan kecil.

78
00:06:50,660 --> 00:06:51,911
Tapi,

79
00:06:51,994 --> 00:06:53,955
kenapa pak cik cakap macam kita sebaya?

80
00:06:54,038 --> 00:06:55,498
Saya jauh lebih muda.

81
00:06:55,581 --> 00:06:58,543
Awak kakak Peguam Han.

82
00:06:59,502 --> 00:07:00,628
Apa?

83
00:07:00,711 --> 00:07:02,880
Awak…

84
00:07:05,842 --> 00:07:08,511
Okey, pak cik silap tadi.

85
00:07:09,345 --> 00:07:10,346
Baru betul.

86
00:07:11,931 --> 00:07:15,309
Sebenarnya, saya bukan
nak buat pak cik ditangkap.

87
00:07:15,852 --> 00:07:16,686
Maaf, ya?

88
00:07:19,689 --> 00:07:23,985
Kalau polis itu datang lagi,
saya minta dia lepaskan pak cik.

89
00:07:24,068 --> 00:07:27,405
Kamu tak perlu tunggu.
Kamu boleh keluar kalau nak.

90
00:07:28,322 --> 00:07:30,450
Apa? Macam mana?

91
00:07:31,284 --> 00:07:32,618
Ini palang keluli…

92
00:07:37,707 --> 00:07:42,879
<i>Dua tiga ikan berenang</i>

93
00:07:47,508 --> 00:07:48,468
Helo?

94
00:07:49,135 --> 00:07:51,053
<i>Ini abang ipar En. Shin I-rang?</i>

95
00:07:51,137 --> 00:07:52,930
Ya, saya. Siapa ini?

96
00:07:53,014 --> 00:07:55,308
Saya Leftenan Cho Chi-yeong
dari Balai Polis Seocho.

97
00:07:56,309 --> 00:07:57,685
Polis?

98
00:07:58,644 --> 00:08:01,147
Kamu dah tenang sikit?

99
00:08:02,648 --> 00:08:04,775
Tak, saya rasa macam nak meletup.

100
00:08:05,485 --> 00:08:07,487
Saya masih muda! Kenapa saya mati?

101
00:08:08,779 --> 00:08:09,739
Ya.

102
00:08:10,406 --> 00:08:11,699
Mesti kamu sedih.

103
00:08:11,782 --> 00:08:14,911
Yang paling teruk,
saya tak ingat apa-apa pun.

104
00:08:15,912 --> 00:08:17,288
Kamu tak ingat?

105
00:08:18,080 --> 00:08:20,041
- Peliknya.
- Kenapa?

106
00:08:20,124 --> 00:08:23,794
Hantu terapung di udara
sampai ingatan mereka pulih.

107
00:08:23,878 --> 00:08:26,130
Tapi kamu dah cecah lantai.

108
00:08:27,256 --> 00:08:31,010
Oh ya, pak cik boleh tolong
pulihkan ingatan kamu.

109
00:08:31,093 --> 00:08:32,094
Macam mana?

110
00:08:32,720 --> 00:08:35,932
Kalau pak cik beritahu kamu
nama dan tarikh lahir kamu…

111
00:08:36,015 --> 00:08:38,017
Beritahu saya cepat.

112
00:08:38,726 --> 00:08:39,936
Ingatan kamu akan pulih.

113
00:08:40,019 --> 00:08:41,604
Pulihkan ingatan saya sekarang!

114
00:08:42,188 --> 00:08:43,564
Okey.

115
00:08:43,648 --> 00:08:46,234
Mula-mula, tarik nafas dalam-dalam.

116
00:08:51,239 --> 00:08:52,573
Cepatlah, pak cik!

117
00:08:52,657 --> 00:08:53,616
Sabarlah.

118
00:08:53,699 --> 00:08:56,452
Kamu panas baran macam adik kamu.

119
00:08:59,956 --> 00:09:02,083
HAN SO-HYUN 19 TAHUN
7 JULAI 2012

120
00:09:06,087 --> 00:09:07,088
Han So-hyun.

121
00:09:13,511 --> 00:09:17,723
Kamu lahir pada 7 Julai 1994.

122
00:09:26,649 --> 00:09:27,692
HAN SO-HYUN

123
00:09:27,775 --> 00:09:28,651
Kakak.

124
00:09:31,028 --> 00:09:32,363
TAEKWONDO HORANG

125
00:09:34,365 --> 00:09:36,158
Hoi! Lepaskan dia!

126
00:09:40,246 --> 00:09:41,372
Mesti seronok.

127
00:09:41,956 --> 00:09:42,832
Na-hyun!

128
00:09:49,630 --> 00:09:50,715
Kakak!

129
00:10:05,313 --> 00:10:06,355
Na-hyun…

130
00:10:13,154 --> 00:10:14,196
Saya…

131
00:10:20,077 --> 00:10:21,662
Saya selamatkan dia.

132
00:10:25,333 --> 00:10:27,627
Saya selamatkan adik saya, Na-hyun.

133
00:10:31,130 --> 00:10:32,214
Ya.

134
00:10:35,968 --> 00:10:38,387
Walaupun dah mati, saya gembira.

135
00:10:41,015 --> 00:10:42,099
Pak cik.

136
00:10:43,559 --> 00:10:44,769
Adik saya

137
00:10:46,020 --> 00:10:48,272
hidup bahagia sekarang, bukan?

138
00:10:52,652 --> 00:10:54,528
Sakitnya kepala.

139
00:10:58,949 --> 00:11:01,202
Banyak sangatkah aku minum?

140
00:11:11,212 --> 00:11:13,339
Kenapa ada jaket Peguam Shin di sini?

141
00:11:23,057 --> 00:11:24,183
Helo?

142
00:11:24,266 --> 00:11:26,477
<i>Peguam Han, tolong adik ipar saya!</i>

143
00:11:27,353 --> 00:11:28,229
Apa?

144
00:11:31,232 --> 00:11:33,067
Sekarang tahun berapa?

145
00:11:34,485 --> 00:11:36,195
2025.

146
00:11:38,447 --> 00:11:40,074
Maknanya…

147
00:11:41,283 --> 00:11:42,576
31 tahun…

148
00:11:44,578 --> 00:11:45,955
Entah-entah dah jadi penyanyi.

149
00:11:47,289 --> 00:11:50,501
Impian adik saya nak jadi penyanyi.

150
00:11:51,085 --> 00:11:52,920
Dulu dia suka menyanyi.

151
00:11:53,003 --> 00:11:55,881
Dia boleh menyanyi
dan main gitar seharian.

152
00:11:57,425 --> 00:11:58,717
Begini.

153
00:11:59,677 --> 00:12:01,804
Adik kamu bukan penyanyi…

154
00:12:01,887 --> 00:12:04,223
En. Shin, peguam awak dah sampai.

155
00:12:11,939 --> 00:12:13,941
Peguam Han…

156
00:12:20,197 --> 00:12:21,198
Han Na-hyun?

157
00:12:25,286 --> 00:12:26,579
Betulkah ini awak?

158
00:12:28,497 --> 00:12:31,041
Apa? Awak jadi peguam?

159
00:12:32,334 --> 00:12:33,294
Kenapa?

160
00:12:36,630 --> 00:12:39,341
Hebatnya.

161
00:12:40,801 --> 00:12:42,678
Budak kecil ini

162
00:12:43,512 --> 00:12:45,890
dah kerja besar sekarang.

163
00:12:49,560 --> 00:12:51,145
Begini perangai awak sebenarnya?

164
00:12:54,732 --> 00:12:57,276
Awak ambil air ini dulu.

165
00:12:58,444 --> 00:12:59,945
Saya tak dahaga.

166
00:13:00,529 --> 00:13:02,573
Cakaplah baik-baik dengan dia.

167
00:13:03,157 --> 00:13:05,201
Saya bukan nak awak minum.

168
00:13:05,910 --> 00:13:09,121
Kalau saya buat pelik-pelik nanti,

169
00:13:09,205 --> 00:13:11,081
percikkan air.

170
00:13:11,165 --> 00:13:12,500
Kenapa pula?

171
00:13:13,209 --> 00:13:15,294
Saya tak macam awak.
Saya tak suka berkasar.

172
00:13:15,377 --> 00:13:17,213
Ya, saya tahu.

173
00:13:18,047 --> 00:13:19,590
Tapi awak peganglah air itu.

174
00:13:20,132 --> 00:13:24,136
Awak boleh percikkan air
kalau saya buat bukan-bukan nanti.

175
00:13:24,220 --> 00:13:26,805
Saya yang minta awak buat.

176
00:13:26,889 --> 00:13:28,474
Itu bukan berkasar.

177
00:13:35,147 --> 00:13:37,107
Mereka macam mana?

178
00:13:37,691 --> 00:13:39,401
Berminggu-minggu baru pulih.

179
00:13:40,569 --> 00:13:42,571
Awak memang suka mabuk teruk begini?

180
00:13:43,489 --> 00:13:45,824
Kenapa berkasar dengan budak sekolah?

181
00:13:45,908 --> 00:13:48,994
Na-hyun, itu bukan salah dia.

182
00:13:49,078 --> 00:13:50,246
Tak tahu nak cakap apa.

183
00:13:50,329 --> 00:13:51,580
Jangan cakap.

184
00:13:52,748 --> 00:13:56,126
Kalau bukan sebab abang ipar awak,
saya tak ambil kes ini.

185
00:13:58,170 --> 00:14:01,674
Saya pun salah sebab minum dengan awak.

186
00:14:01,757 --> 00:14:04,301
Terima kasih sebab jadi peguam saya.

187
00:14:05,678 --> 00:14:09,974
Tapi tiga budak pukul seorang budak.

188
00:14:10,891 --> 00:14:12,184
Bukan itu yang saya dengar.

189
00:14:13,102 --> 00:14:15,312
Mereka berborak saja.

190
00:14:15,980 --> 00:14:17,856
Awak tiba-tiba serang budak itu.

191
00:14:20,359 --> 00:14:21,944
Taklah!

192
00:14:22,027 --> 00:14:24,655
Sumpah, tiga budak buli seorang budak.

193
00:14:24,738 --> 00:14:27,116
Mereka serang saya dulu.

194
00:14:29,034 --> 00:14:31,579
Tiga budak buli seorang budak.

195
00:14:31,662 --> 00:14:33,581
Mereka serang saya dulu.

196
00:14:33,664 --> 00:14:35,791
Keempat-empat mangsa beri keterangan sama.

197
00:14:36,584 --> 00:14:40,129
Kalau awak nafikan lagi,
mereka nak saman jenayah dan sivil.

198
00:14:41,088 --> 00:14:44,717
Kalau tak selesaikan dengan ibu bapa
Sung Min-jae yang pulih empat minggu lagi,

199
00:14:44,800 --> 00:14:46,594
awak dihukum penjara minimum enam bulan.

200
00:14:47,761 --> 00:14:49,430
Kemudian, hilang lesen guaman.

201
00:14:50,014 --> 00:14:53,517
Jangan terus buat kesimpulan
tanpa usul periksa.

202
00:14:55,561 --> 00:14:57,479
Awak tak percayakan saya?

203
00:14:57,563 --> 00:14:59,231
Lebih baik selesaikan saja.

204
00:14:59,732 --> 00:15:02,735
Selesaikan tak kira apa.

205
00:15:02,818 --> 00:15:04,403
Hei, awak tak tahu apa-apa!

206
00:15:06,155 --> 00:15:07,239
Nanti saya selesaikan.

207
00:15:07,323 --> 00:15:08,908
Pastikan selesai.

208
00:15:11,493 --> 00:15:14,330
Nasib baik waran tangkap ditarik balik.

209
00:15:14,413 --> 00:15:15,748
Awak balik dulu.

210
00:15:17,374 --> 00:15:18,959
Awak peguam apa?

211
00:15:21,795 --> 00:15:25,549
Peguam kena dengar cerita
anak guam dan menyebelahi mereka.

212
00:15:27,384 --> 00:15:28,802
Kenapa nak marah pula?

213
00:15:28,886 --> 00:15:30,429
Jangan layan anak guam begini!

214
00:15:30,512 --> 00:15:32,640
Beginikah Han Na-hyun yang saya kenal?

215
00:15:33,390 --> 00:15:34,808
Han Na-hyun yang saya kenal?

216
00:15:35,684 --> 00:15:38,437
Bila awak kenal saya? Jaga mulut sikit.

217
00:15:38,520 --> 00:15:39,939
Dah mabuk, pukul budak.

218
00:15:40,564 --> 00:15:42,983
Sebab mereka patut dipukul!

219
00:15:43,067 --> 00:15:45,319
Peguam mana yang cakap begitu?

220
00:15:45,402 --> 00:15:48,113
Sejak bila awak tegas begini? Kacaulah!

221
00:15:57,289 --> 00:15:58,374
Kacaulah?

222
00:16:22,523 --> 00:16:25,359
Kamu cakap apa dengan adik kamu?

223
00:16:26,026 --> 00:16:27,820
Saya cakap dia kacau.

224
00:16:28,529 --> 00:16:29,571
Apa?

225
00:16:30,864 --> 00:16:33,325
Maaf. Saya tak sengaja.

226
00:16:35,035 --> 00:16:37,037
Tapi dia yang salah.

227
00:16:37,121 --> 00:16:40,541
Pak cik pun tak suka
orang yang pukul budak sekolah.

228
00:16:40,624 --> 00:16:41,875
Bukan.

229
00:16:41,959 --> 00:16:45,212
Dia yang tak patut marah
tanpa usul periksa.

230
00:16:45,295 --> 00:16:47,631
Tapi peliklah dia jadi peguam.

231
00:16:47,715 --> 00:16:50,384
Kalau rasa pelik, kenapa tak kejar dia?

232
00:16:51,385 --> 00:16:52,386
Pak cik macam mana?

233
00:16:52,970 --> 00:16:55,347
Waran ditarik balik.
Nanti mereka lepaskan pak cik.

234
00:16:55,973 --> 00:16:57,307
Kamu pergilah.

235
00:17:05,774 --> 00:17:09,361
<i>- Di langit biru indah</i>
- Aduh, dia mula dah.

236
00:17:09,445 --> 00:17:12,656
<i>- Terbang dengan karpet ajaib</i>
<i>- Karpet ajaib</i>

237
00:17:12,740 --> 00:17:14,950
<i>- Di dunia biru</i>
<i>- Di dunia biru</i>

238
00:17:15,034 --> 00:17:17,161
- Ayah, pandang depan!
- <i>Yang indah</i>

239
00:17:18,245 --> 00:17:19,955
Awak tak suka dengar muzik sekarang?

240
00:17:21,915 --> 00:17:23,333
AYAH

241
00:17:28,172 --> 00:17:29,381
AYAH

242
00:17:34,720 --> 00:17:36,555
Kenapa awak lain sangat sekarang?

243
00:17:41,226 --> 00:17:42,227
Wah.

244
00:17:43,479 --> 00:17:45,314
Kawasan rumah aku tak berubah langsung.

245
00:17:46,940 --> 00:17:48,067
Baguslah.

246
00:18:07,127 --> 00:18:08,128
Ayah?

247
00:18:22,726 --> 00:18:25,187
Dah banyak uban sekarang.

248
00:18:27,731 --> 00:18:29,191
Muka dah berkedut.

249
00:18:36,615 --> 00:18:39,243
TIDAK BEROPERASI

250
00:18:44,081 --> 00:18:46,250
Tapi saya seronok…

251
00:18:48,836 --> 00:18:50,045
dapat jumpa ayah.

252
00:19:06,478 --> 00:19:08,814
Sayang, saya dah balik.

253
00:19:14,444 --> 00:19:15,946
Kusyen ini masih ada.

254
00:19:16,613 --> 00:19:18,448
Tapi sofa dah baru.

255
00:19:19,366 --> 00:19:20,284
Cantik.

256
00:19:20,367 --> 00:19:22,744
Sedapnya bau.

257
00:19:22,828 --> 00:19:24,705
Awak dah balik. Mesti lapar.

258
00:19:24,788 --> 00:19:26,707
- Pergi basuh tangan.
- Okey.

259
00:19:39,219 --> 00:19:40,387
Mak.

260
00:19:49,521 --> 00:19:50,689
Mak.

261
00:20:05,787 --> 00:20:06,997
Wah.

262
00:20:07,080 --> 00:20:09,666
Sedapnya tauhu tumis mak.

263
00:20:11,293 --> 00:20:13,795
Stu <i>doenjang</i> itu pun nampak sedap.

264
00:20:14,922 --> 00:20:16,757
Begitulah awak, minum soju kosong lagi.

265
00:20:16,840 --> 00:20:18,967
Saya dah kata, kena makan bersulam soju.

266
00:20:19,051 --> 00:20:21,303
- Okey.
- Nah.

267
00:20:22,679 --> 00:20:25,224
Awak dah telefon Na-hyun?

268
00:20:25,307 --> 00:20:28,644
Dah, tapi dia kata nak makan di luar saja.

269
00:20:29,811 --> 00:20:30,729
Okey.

270
00:20:32,189 --> 00:20:33,023
Kenapa?

271
00:20:33,649 --> 00:20:35,651
Sedih sebab tak boleh masak
untuk anak kita?

272
00:20:35,734 --> 00:20:37,569
Taklah, bukan itu.

273
00:20:39,446 --> 00:20:41,198
Saya rasa kita kena pindah.

274
00:20:43,450 --> 00:20:45,410
Saya rasa dia nak elak rumah ini.

275
00:20:45,494 --> 00:20:47,788
Aduh, taklah.

276
00:20:47,871 --> 00:20:50,415
Dia yang sibuk.

277
00:20:50,499 --> 00:20:52,584
Kira baguslah dia ada masa untuk kita.

278
00:20:54,294 --> 00:20:55,837
- Yakah?
- Ya.

279
00:20:57,923 --> 00:21:01,176
Jangan fikir bukan-bukan.

280
00:21:01,260 --> 00:21:02,886
Jangan cakap baik-baik dengan dia.

281
00:21:03,845 --> 00:21:05,472
Samalah orang itu pun.

282
00:21:05,555 --> 00:21:06,848
Aduh.

283
00:21:07,599 --> 00:21:09,726
Berita dah mula. Pukul berapa sekarang?

284
00:21:10,310 --> 00:21:11,144
Aduh.

285
00:21:12,437 --> 00:21:14,606
Han Na-hyun tak suka rumah ini?

286
00:21:16,400 --> 00:21:19,653
Mak dan ayah kena
cakap baik-baik dengan dia?

287
00:21:21,863 --> 00:21:22,864
Kenapa?

288
00:21:24,950 --> 00:21:26,618
Kenapa kena begitu?

289
00:21:28,120 --> 00:21:30,205
- Belakang kau.
- Tahu. Aku dengar.

290
00:21:30,289 --> 00:21:31,206
Dia gerak.

291
00:21:31,290 --> 00:21:33,709
- Aku nampak.
- Cepat. Dia laju.

292
00:21:33,792 --> 00:21:35,210
- Nyawa tinggal satu.
- Okey.

293
00:21:35,294 --> 00:21:37,170
- Matilah dia.
- Tembak dia.

294
00:21:37,254 --> 00:21:39,131
- Ke kanan sikit.
- Mana dia?

295
00:21:39,214 --> 00:21:42,718
- Sekejap. Aku tolong.
- Aduh.

296
00:21:42,801 --> 00:21:43,635
Helo?

297
00:21:43,719 --> 00:21:45,470
Habis peluru pula.

298
00:21:46,680 --> 00:21:47,889
Kita berkumpul.

299
00:21:47,973 --> 00:21:49,725
- Mana kau?
- Sekejap. Aduh.

300
00:21:49,808 --> 00:21:51,393
Mesti seronok ponteng sekolah.

301
00:21:52,102 --> 00:21:53,437
Tak perlu mengadap cikgu.

302
00:21:54,104 --> 00:21:55,188
Pak cik siapa?

303
00:21:55,272 --> 00:21:56,648
Saya Peguam Yang Do-kyung.

304
00:21:56,732 --> 00:21:59,443
Peguam? Maknanya, kita bos dia?

305
00:21:59,526 --> 00:22:01,111
Ya, mestilah.

306
00:22:02,112 --> 00:22:03,989
En. Peguam, kami sibuk sekarang.

307
00:22:04,072 --> 00:22:05,115
Gilalah.

308
00:22:05,782 --> 00:22:06,908
Lain kali saja.

309
00:22:09,286 --> 00:22:13,915
Sibuk betul kamu.
Sebab itulah ibu bapa kamu upah saya.

310
00:22:15,500 --> 00:22:19,212
Mereka marah sebab
anak kesayangan mereka dipukul,

311
00:22:19,713 --> 00:22:22,883
walaupun tak tahu apa kamu buat
kepada Jun-ho sepanjang tahun ini.

312
00:22:29,681 --> 00:22:31,224
Apa jadi hari itu?

313
00:22:35,604 --> 00:22:37,647
Kami dah beritahu polis semuanya.

314
00:22:37,731 --> 00:22:42,152
Kami main-main saja. Tiba-tiba,
orang gila itu datang dan serang kami.

315
00:22:42,861 --> 00:22:44,946
- Kamu tipu.
- Tak, betul.

316
00:22:45,030 --> 00:22:46,531
Ada sesuatu yang kamu kena tahu.

317
00:22:47,657 --> 00:22:50,410
Orang yang pukul kamu itu upah peguam.

318
00:22:50,494 --> 00:22:53,622
Peguam yang dia upah itu
peguam nombor satu.

319
00:22:54,498 --> 00:22:55,665
Sekejap saja

320
00:22:56,750 --> 00:22:58,335
dia boleh tahu apa kamu buat.

321
00:23:02,839 --> 00:23:03,965
Mesti awak Min-jae.

322
00:23:06,259 --> 00:23:08,386
Ayah, Timbalan Menteri
Kesihatan dan Kebajikan.

323
00:23:09,012 --> 00:23:11,848
Ji-hyeok, mak awak
profesor perundangan Universiti Hanguk.

324
00:23:13,308 --> 00:23:17,229
Ibu bapa kamu akan dapat masalah
kalau kebenaran terbongkar.

325
00:23:17,312 --> 00:23:18,563
Mesti mereka mengamuk.

326
00:23:22,651 --> 00:23:23,568
Betul.

327
00:23:24,444 --> 00:23:27,155
Sekarang, kamu kena
cakap jujur dengan saya.

328
00:23:28,240 --> 00:23:29,991
Barulah saya boleh lindungi kamu.

329
00:23:31,076 --> 00:23:33,954
Saya tak peduli kamu belasah orang.

330
00:23:34,788 --> 00:23:36,081
Yang saya nak tahu,

331
00:23:36,164 --> 00:23:38,625
peguam yang serang kamu itu.

332
00:23:39,835 --> 00:23:42,921
Kamu tak rasa dia pelik?

333
00:24:52,240 --> 00:24:53,575
FAIL
TEMPAT LETAK KERETA

334
00:25:29,361 --> 00:25:31,029
Mak pun dah tahu?

335
00:25:33,198 --> 00:25:35,992
Dia terdengar saya dan Sa-rang
cakap tentang duit penyelesaian…

336
00:25:36,576 --> 00:25:38,078
Kakak pun tahu?

337
00:25:40,956 --> 00:25:42,582
Semua orang dah tahu.

338
00:25:44,000 --> 00:25:46,836
Mak cakap dia akan cari duit.

339
00:25:47,462 --> 00:25:51,883
Selepas dengar awak boleh
hilang lesen guaman,

340
00:25:51,967 --> 00:25:54,094
dia meluru keluar.

341
00:25:55,553 --> 00:25:57,555
Tapi dia tak jadi marah selepas tahu

342
00:25:57,639 --> 00:25:59,975
awak dirasuk kakak Peguam Han.

343
00:26:00,058 --> 00:26:05,397
Saya dan kakak awak akan cuba
cari duit juga, jangan risau.

344
00:26:08,900 --> 00:26:10,193
- Bong-su.
- Ya?

345
00:26:11,987 --> 00:26:13,071
Saya minta maaf.

346
00:26:13,863 --> 00:26:14,698
Terima kasih.

347
00:26:43,018 --> 00:26:44,019
Saya minta maaf.

348
00:26:46,146 --> 00:26:48,315
Mungkin saya tak patut datang.

349
00:26:49,232 --> 00:26:51,860
Pak cik dapat masalah disebabkan saya.

350
00:26:52,819 --> 00:26:55,572
Saya pula dapat tahu
sesuatu yang tak elok.

351
00:26:56,614 --> 00:26:58,742
Apa yang kamu dapat tahu?

352
00:27:00,869 --> 00:27:04,414
Ada yang kena
antara Na-hyun dan mak ayah saya.

353
00:27:05,749 --> 00:27:08,460
Keluarga saya tak kaya,

354
00:27:08,918 --> 00:27:10,837
tapi kami suka gelak dan berseronok.

355
00:27:10,920 --> 00:27:12,630
Hidup kami selalu ceria.

356
00:27:13,715 --> 00:27:16,634
Sekarang, mak ayah saya
kena cakap baik-baik dengan Na-hyun.

357
00:27:17,427 --> 00:27:19,220
Na-hyun pun pelik.

358
00:27:21,556 --> 00:27:24,100
Entah apa jadi.

359
00:27:24,684 --> 00:27:26,186
Memang ada sesuatu terjadi.

360
00:27:27,937 --> 00:27:31,358
Mereka kehilangan kamu,
ahli keluarga tersayang.

361
00:27:32,525 --> 00:27:34,319
Mesti mereka sedih.

362
00:27:38,948 --> 00:27:42,577
Kenapa keluarga jadi renggang
semasa sedih?

363
00:27:42,660 --> 00:27:44,788
Pak cik tak rasa mereka berenggang.

364
00:27:46,456 --> 00:27:47,874
Mungkin mereka nak jaga hati.

365
00:27:49,084 --> 00:27:50,085
Jaga hati?

366
00:27:52,212 --> 00:27:53,922
Ada sesetengah kesedihan

367
00:27:54,672 --> 00:27:58,802
terlalu besar sampai boleh
merebak ke orang sekeliling.

368
00:28:06,059 --> 00:28:09,062
KISAH BAHAGIA BERPANJANGAN

369
00:28:14,943 --> 00:28:17,237
<i>Kita risau orang sekeliling pun sedih,</i>

370
00:28:17,821 --> 00:28:19,864
<i>jadi kita pendam perasaan,</i>

371
00:28:20,573 --> 00:28:22,867
<i>jaga percakapan atau kelakuan,</i>

372
00:28:24,035 --> 00:28:25,078
<i>kadang-kadang,</i>

373
00:28:25,995 --> 00:28:27,789
<i>terpaksa berahsia.</i>

374
00:28:30,542 --> 00:28:33,169
Kita tak nak orang sekeliling pun terluka,

375
00:28:33,753 --> 00:28:36,464
sampai kita jauhi mereka
sedikit demi sedikit.

376
00:28:38,842 --> 00:28:42,679
Saya tak nak keluarga saya
hidup begini disebabkan saya.

377
00:28:45,890 --> 00:28:47,308
Sedihnya.

378
00:28:50,687 --> 00:28:55,400
Semua hantu yang jumpa pak cik
ada kisah sedih.

379
00:28:56,067 --> 00:28:57,527
Tapi semuanya okey selepas itu.

380
00:28:58,611 --> 00:29:00,530
Sekarang kamu dah datang.

381
00:29:00,613 --> 00:29:03,032
Mungkin keluarga kamu
boleh lebih saling terbuka.

382
00:29:03,867 --> 00:29:06,870
Pak cik akan cuba yang terbaik
untuk tolong kamu.

383
00:29:09,164 --> 00:29:10,165
Terima kasih.

384
00:29:13,543 --> 00:29:15,754
Tapi masalah pak cik lebih serius.

385
00:29:16,629 --> 00:29:17,505
Masalah apa?

386
00:29:18,089 --> 00:29:20,884
Entah macam mana saya nak hidup
kalau pak cik hilang rumah

387
00:29:20,967 --> 00:29:22,051
dan kerja sebab saya.

388
00:29:22,135 --> 00:29:23,511
Sekejap.

389
00:29:23,595 --> 00:29:25,096
Tapi saya dah mati.

390
00:29:26,431 --> 00:29:27,348
Tak apalah.

391
00:29:29,809 --> 00:29:30,810
Kamu

392
00:29:32,020 --> 00:29:32,937
memang baik.

393
00:29:33,021 --> 00:29:35,523
Mana boleh biarkan benda yang salah.

394
00:29:36,649 --> 00:29:39,152
Macam mana nak bersihkan nama pak cik?

395
00:29:40,904 --> 00:29:43,406
Kalau betul apa yang kamu nampak hari itu,

396
00:29:43,490 --> 00:29:47,827
mesti ada sebab Jun-ho berlagak
macam dia bukan mangsa buli.

397
00:29:48,411 --> 00:29:51,080
Kamu kena siasat.

398
00:29:51,831 --> 00:29:52,791
Apa? Saya?

399
00:29:52,874 --> 00:29:54,042
Ya.

400
00:29:54,125 --> 00:29:55,210
Macam mana?

401
00:29:56,669 --> 00:29:58,338
Nama pun hantu.

402
00:30:18,107 --> 00:30:20,276
- Helo.
- Helo.

403
00:30:21,945 --> 00:30:22,946
Helo.

404
00:30:38,753 --> 00:30:41,047
Maaf, saya tak tahu.

405
00:31:00,441 --> 00:31:02,026
SUNG MIN-JAE

406
00:31:12,078 --> 00:31:14,330
- Helo…
<i>- Kenapa lambat angkat?</i>

407
00:31:16,541 --> 00:31:17,458
Maaf.

408
00:31:17,542 --> 00:31:19,002
Kau jumpa siapa hari ini?

409
00:31:19,586 --> 00:31:20,837
Aku tak jumpa sesiapa.

410
00:31:20,920 --> 00:31:22,922
Kalau kau tipu, aku bunuh kau betul-betul.

411
00:31:24,507 --> 00:31:25,758
Betul.

412
00:31:29,512 --> 00:31:31,764
Datang ke Kafe Siber Langit dan Bumi
pukul 5.00.

413
00:31:31,848 --> 00:31:33,099
Jangan lupa duit.

414
00:31:34,017 --> 00:31:35,226
Okey.

415
00:31:50,158 --> 00:31:52,368
Kenapa kau buat aku begini?

416
00:31:54,412 --> 00:31:55,496
Apa salah aku…

417
00:31:56,497 --> 00:31:58,082
dapat nasib begini?

418
00:32:07,884 --> 00:32:09,093
Aku nak bunuh mereka.

419
00:32:20,605 --> 00:32:21,731
Siapa?

420
00:32:25,902 --> 00:32:27,862
Helo, saya Peguam Han Na-hyun.

421
00:32:28,488 --> 00:32:29,322
Peguam?

422
00:32:29,989 --> 00:32:31,699
Puan ibu Jun-ho?

423
00:32:32,825 --> 00:32:33,701
Ya.

424
00:32:34,577 --> 00:32:36,955
Ada apa-apa jadi dengan anak saya?

425
00:32:38,039 --> 00:32:39,749
Dia tak cakap apa-apa dengan puan?

426
00:32:40,833 --> 00:32:44,170
Saya jarang jumpa dia
sebab saya kerja malam.

427
00:32:45,171 --> 00:32:46,881
Dia buat masalah?

428
00:32:46,965 --> 00:32:47,799
Tak.

429
00:32:48,383 --> 00:32:51,970
Anak puan terlibat dalam kes kecil,
tapi dia bukan penyerang.

430
00:32:54,305 --> 00:32:57,642
Puan tahu dia di mana sekarang?

431
00:33:05,108 --> 00:33:06,109
Jun-ho.

432
00:33:20,331 --> 00:33:23,251
Pak cik nampak hari itu.

433
00:33:24,127 --> 00:33:25,461
Mereka buli kamu.

434
00:33:26,045 --> 00:33:28,673
Tak, mereka kawan saya.

435
00:33:29,716 --> 00:33:31,926
- Kami main-main saja.
- Mereka bukan…

436
00:33:33,052 --> 00:33:34,178
kawan kamu.

437
00:33:34,846 --> 00:33:35,680
Kamu pun tahu.

438
00:33:35,763 --> 00:33:37,265
Saya tak tahu pak cik cakap apa.

439
00:33:37,348 --> 00:33:38,850
- Jun-ho.
- Saya nak pergi.

440
00:33:39,434 --> 00:33:40,476
Hei, Seo Jun-ho!

441
00:33:45,690 --> 00:33:47,025
Jadi, apa kau nak buat?

442
00:33:47,817 --> 00:33:48,860
Apa?

443
00:33:48,943 --> 00:33:51,029
Apa kau nak buat? Kau nak bunuh mereka?

444
00:33:54,240 --> 00:33:55,408
Dulu,

445
00:33:56,409 --> 00:33:58,327
ada budak macam kau di sekolah aku.

446
00:33:59,787 --> 00:34:01,956
Dia teruk dibuli,

447
00:34:02,874 --> 00:34:05,209
tapi mak ayah dan cikgu dia tak tahu,

448
00:34:05,293 --> 00:34:07,587
apatah lagi budak kelas dia.

449
00:34:07,670 --> 00:34:08,880
Jadi?

450
00:34:08,963 --> 00:34:10,715
Apa gunanya cerita itu?

451
00:34:10,798 --> 00:34:13,217
Nak tahu kenapa pembuli suka ada geng?

452
00:34:13,968 --> 00:34:15,178
Sebab mereka pengecut.

453
00:34:16,095 --> 00:34:17,930
Jadi, jangan terus lari.

454
00:34:18,014 --> 00:34:20,308
Kau lawan balik kalau mereka kacau.

455
00:34:20,391 --> 00:34:22,393
Tak, aku tak boleh.

456
00:34:22,477 --> 00:34:24,312
Tiada yang mustahil.

457
00:34:24,395 --> 00:34:26,981
- Kau kena kuatkan…
- Aku tak boleh, okey?

458
00:34:27,607 --> 00:34:29,525
Aku kata tak boleh!

459
00:34:36,949 --> 00:34:39,202
Jangan kata…

460
00:34:40,787 --> 00:34:42,789
Mereka peras ugut kau?

461
00:34:46,000 --> 00:34:46,918
Aku nak pergi.

462
00:34:47,752 --> 00:34:48,961
Itu saja kau nak kata?

463
00:34:49,796 --> 00:34:50,630
Nak kata apa lagi?

464
00:34:51,589 --> 00:34:53,758
Kalau aku kata, boleh aku bunuh mereka?

465
00:34:56,260 --> 00:34:58,262
- Helo, Jun-ho.
- Jun-ho, hai!

466
00:34:58,346 --> 00:35:01,224
Aku rasa nak buat filem panas hari ini.

467
00:35:01,307 --> 00:35:03,726
- Lepaslah.
- Lampu, sedia?

468
00:35:03,810 --> 00:35:06,437
- Hei, lampu.
- Sekejap.

469
00:35:06,521 --> 00:35:08,106
Semua sedia.

470
00:35:08,189 --> 00:35:10,399
Cantik pula dia hari ini.

471
00:35:10,483 --> 00:35:13,444
- Jangan.
- Duduk diam sekejap, Jun-ho.

472
00:35:14,028 --> 00:35:15,655
Mereka ugut kau dengan video itu.

473
00:35:17,240 --> 00:35:18,116
Ya.

474
00:35:19,117 --> 00:35:22,370
Mereka rakam aku bertelanjang.

475
00:35:36,717 --> 00:35:39,637
Tapi kau tak patut buat macam mereka.

476
00:35:40,847 --> 00:35:42,849
Budak yang aku cakap tadi

477
00:35:42,932 --> 00:35:44,934
masuk sekolah juvana

478
00:35:45,810 --> 00:35:48,020
selepas pukul pembuli dia dengan bata.

479
00:35:49,021 --> 00:35:53,276
Tak ada orang faham
kenapa dia serang mereka.

480
00:35:54,277 --> 00:35:55,778
Kau pun boleh jadi macam dia.

481
00:35:56,696 --> 00:35:58,698
Kalau ikut hati, boleh merana lagi.

482
00:35:59,949 --> 00:36:01,409
Jadi, tolonglah.

483
