00:53:29,998 --> 00:53:32,417
ditahan atas serangan teruk, rakaman haram

723
00:53:32,500 --> 00:53:34,336
dan pengedaran kandungan haram.

724
00:53:35,337 --> 00:53:39,007
Mereka juga belasah Seo Jun-ho
pada hari kes serangan itu.

725
00:53:39,716 --> 00:53:42,636
Lee Seo-won mengaku
yang Peguam Shin I-rang

726
00:53:42,719 --> 00:53:44,095
cuma nak hentikan mereka.

727
00:53:44,971 --> 00:53:46,514
Awak cakap apa?

728
00:53:47,057 --> 00:53:47,891
Helo?

729
00:53:48,642 --> 00:53:49,851
Polis?

730
00:53:49,935 --> 00:53:51,061
- Helo?
- Min-jae.

731
00:53:51,144 --> 00:53:52,437
Mak datang sekarang.

732
00:53:52,520 --> 00:53:54,314
Kamu buat apa lagi?

733
00:53:57,776 --> 00:54:00,362
Anak puan dah nak sampai.
Puan tunggu dia di bawah.

734
00:54:00,445 --> 00:54:02,405
Terima kasih, Cik Peguam.

735
00:54:15,502 --> 00:54:17,462
Awak tak nak cakap apa-apa?

736
00:54:19,297 --> 00:54:20,632
Nak cakap apa?

737
00:54:20,715 --> 00:54:23,009
Saya dengar awak suruh
mereka buang telefon lama.

738
00:54:23,551 --> 00:54:24,386
Betulkah?

739
00:54:26,972 --> 00:54:28,223
Nak hairan apa?

740
00:54:29,057 --> 00:54:32,268
Awak pun sanggup buat apa saja
untuk menang kes.

741
00:54:32,352 --> 00:54:33,687
Itulah cara awak, bukan?

742
00:54:39,359 --> 00:54:40,944
Saya ingat

743
00:54:41,027 --> 00:54:42,654
kita sehaluan.

744
00:54:46,157 --> 00:54:47,409
Awak masih macam dulu.

745
00:54:49,619 --> 00:54:50,912
Ini sebab Shin I-rang?

746
00:54:54,416 --> 00:54:55,750
Sebab dia awak berubah?

747
00:54:55,834 --> 00:54:56,876
Jangan sibuk.

748
00:54:56,960 --> 00:54:59,838
Lee Gang-pung, Kim Su-a, Jeon Sang-ho.

749
00:55:00,797 --> 00:55:02,090
Semuanya dah mati.

750
00:55:02,173 --> 00:55:03,091
Jadi?

751
00:55:03,174 --> 00:55:06,011
Semua anak guam dia keluarga orang mati.

752
00:55:07,012 --> 00:55:09,014
Kenapa dia cuma ambil kes begitu?

753
00:55:09,597 --> 00:55:11,933
Kenapa dia selalu terlibat
dengan orang mati?

754
00:55:12,517 --> 00:55:15,603
Dia mencarut macam Lee Gang-pung
dan berlagak macam Kim Su-a.

755
00:55:15,687 --> 00:55:18,273
Macam mana dia tahu
tempat mayat Jeon Sang-ho ditanam?

756
00:55:18,356 --> 00:55:19,941
Sikit pun awak tak rasa pelik?

757
00:55:25,530 --> 00:55:26,865
Sebelum ini,

758
00:55:28,575 --> 00:55:30,577
{\an8}pejabat dia bekas rumah bomoh.

759
00:55:32,037 --> 00:55:34,622
Shin I-rang boleh nampak hantu.

760
00:55:35,290 --> 00:55:36,708
Bahaya kalau dekat dengan dia.

761
00:55:38,585 --> 00:55:39,794
Jangan cakap mengarut.

762
00:56:19,501 --> 00:56:20,418
KHAMIS, 7 JUN 2012

763
00:56:20,502 --> 00:56:22,337
<i>Entah siapa lebih bersalah.</i>

764
00:56:22,420 --> 00:56:24,130
<i>Orang yang pukul dengan bata?</i>

765
00:56:24,214 --> 00:56:26,591
<i>Atau yang buli dia sampai mati?</i>

766
00:56:26,674 --> 00:56:28,343
<i>Dia terpaksa…</i>

767
00:56:28,426 --> 00:56:29,677
<i>Kalau jadi peguam terbaik,</i>

768
00:56:29,761 --> 00:56:31,012
<i>bolehkah aku faham dia?</i>

769
00:56:31,096 --> 00:56:32,097
<i>Kalau jadi peguam terbaik,</i>

770
00:56:32,180 --> 00:56:36,184
<i>bolehkah aku faham penderitaan dia?</i>

771
00:56:38,561 --> 00:56:40,897
Tak ada orang faham

772
00:56:41,940 --> 00:56:43,274
kenapa dia serang mereka.

773
00:56:43,358 --> 00:56:47,779
<i>Siapa yang boleh faham</i>
<i>mangsa yang terpaksa serang mereka?</i>

774
00:57:00,291 --> 00:57:04,129
{\an8}Sebelum ini,
pejabat dia bekas rumah bomoh.

775
00:57:04,212 --> 00:57:07,340
Pejabat saya pula bekas rumah bomoh.

776
00:57:33,491 --> 00:57:35,118
ANAK, NA-HYUN

777
00:57:36,161 --> 00:57:37,287
Hai, Na-hyun.

778
00:57:37,370 --> 00:57:40,039
- Kamu…
<i>- Mak pernah pergi ke rumah bomoh?</i>

779
00:57:41,332 --> 00:57:42,208
Apa?

780
00:57:42,292 --> 00:57:45,879
Mak ada jumpa bomoh selepas insiden itu?

781
00:57:46,796 --> 00:57:49,174
Macam mana kamu…

782
00:57:49,257 --> 00:57:50,967
Di Seocho-dong?

783
00:57:59,058 --> 00:58:01,895
Saya boleh nampak
dan berkomunikasi dengan orang mati.

784
00:58:01,978 --> 00:58:03,605
Kali ini, roh Su-a.

785
00:58:03,688 --> 00:58:06,608
Dulu, roh Lee Gang-pung tolong saya.

786
00:58:10,320 --> 00:58:11,863
<i>Jangan layan anak guam begini!</i>

787
00:58:11,946 --> 00:58:13,615
<i>Beginikah Han Na-hyun yang saya kenal?</i>

788
00:58:13,698 --> 00:58:16,618
Sejak bila awak tegas begini? Kacaulah!

789
00:58:20,455 --> 00:58:21,539
Kakak.

790
00:58:22,832 --> 00:58:24,042
Tak mungkin.

791
00:58:29,422 --> 00:58:34,260
{\an8}BBQ KEDAI DAGING DUB-DUB

792
00:58:36,763 --> 00:58:38,014
Maaf, mak.

793
00:58:38,681 --> 00:58:41,309
Peguam Han tahu kakak dia dah datang?

794
00:58:41,893 --> 00:58:42,810
Tak.

795
00:58:43,520 --> 00:58:45,146
Saya tak tahu nak buat apa.

796
00:58:45,730 --> 00:58:47,357
Mesti dia terkejut kalau tahu.

797
00:58:48,066 --> 00:58:50,485
Mungkin elok saya rahsiakan saja.

798
00:58:53,613 --> 00:58:55,573
Dari dulu dia banyak tolong kita.

799
00:58:55,657 --> 00:58:57,575
Kita kena belanja dia makan.

800
00:58:58,117 --> 00:58:59,953
Nanti tanya bila dia boleh datang.

801
00:59:02,872 --> 00:59:03,706
Okey.

802
00:59:23,851 --> 00:59:25,144
Kamu buat apa di sini?

803
00:59:45,039 --> 00:59:46,040
Na-hyun.

804
00:59:50,962 --> 00:59:51,963
Peguam Han?

805
00:59:52,880 --> 00:59:54,799
Saya memang nak telefon awak.

806
00:59:54,882 --> 00:59:56,301
Awak sibuk sekarang?

807
00:59:57,510 --> 00:59:58,761
Kenapa awak tanya?

808
00:59:58,845 --> 01:00:00,430
Saya nak ajak awak ke satu tempat.

809
01:00:14,193 --> 01:00:16,154
Awak nak kita naik kuda itu?

810
01:00:17,113 --> 01:00:18,239
Awak tak nak?

811
01:00:18,323 --> 01:00:20,783
Tak, bukan tak nak.

812
01:00:22,327 --> 01:00:23,453
Baguslah.

813
01:00:24,120 --> 01:00:25,163
Saya pergi beli tiket.

814
01:00:30,126 --> 01:00:32,211
Saya takut tinggi.

815
01:00:36,633 --> 01:00:39,260
Kamu suka?

816
01:00:39,344 --> 01:00:41,179
Saya suka gila!

817
01:00:42,722 --> 01:00:44,182
Sekejap.

818
01:00:45,850 --> 01:00:49,395
Peguam Han tahu kamu suka <i>roller coaster?</i>

819
01:00:49,479 --> 01:00:51,981
Mestilah! Dulu kami kerap ke sini
setiap kali cuti.

820
01:00:54,609 --> 01:00:55,652
Jadi, dia…

821
01:00:56,694 --> 01:00:58,154
bawa pak cik ke sini…

822
01:01:02,742 --> 01:01:04,744
KAUNTER TIKET

823
01:01:21,928 --> 01:01:23,096
Na-hyun.

824
01:01:29,268 --> 01:01:32,021
Jom duduk di belakang sekali hari ini.

825
01:01:32,105 --> 01:01:33,856
- Angkat tangan.
- Angkat tangan. Nak?

826
01:01:53,209 --> 01:01:54,168
Kakak.

827
01:02:51,017 --> 01:02:53,019
{\an8}<i>- Kakak?</i>
- I-rang.

828
01:02:53,102 --> 01:02:55,438
{\an8}Saya nak berdua dengan dia
tanpa awak hari ini.

829
01:02:55,521 --> 01:02:56,397
{\an8}<i>Jangan risau.</i>

830
01:02:56,481 --> 01:02:58,858
{\an8}Kasihan Na-hyun.

831
01:02:58,941 --> 01:03:00,818
{\an8}<i>Saya tak patut ada di sini.</i>

832
01:03:00,902 --> 01:03:02,361
{\an8}Tak apakah pergi begini?

833
01:03:02,445 --> 01:03:04,781
{\an8}Saya tak nak hati dia remuk lagi.

834
01:03:04,864 --> 01:03:06,824
{\an8}<i>Begitu. Maaf sebab tak bertimbang rasa.</i>

835
01:03:08,242 --> 01:03:09,160
{\an8}Mana So-hyun?

836
01:03:09,243 --> 01:03:10,578
{\an8}<i>Mereka semua pergi.</i>

837
01:03:10,661 --> 01:03:12,705
{\an8}<i>- Tidak.</i>
<i>- Jaga diri.</i>

838
01:03:13,289 --> 01:03:14,415
{\an8}<i>Jangan pergi.</i>

839
01:03:15,374 --> 01:03:19,295
{\an8}Terjemahan sari kata oleh Aizat Bahri

